#. Tag: para
#: apps_librewriter.xml:749
#, no-c-format
msgid "To attach your style, make sure your page is a left (even) page and double-click <guimenu>Left Content Page</guimenu> . Whenever your text exceeds the length of a page, the following page automatically receives the alternative page style."
