#. Tag: para
#: apps_librewriter.xml:775
#, no-c-format
msgid "To open the Navigator, click <menuchoice> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenu>Navigator</guimenu> </menuchoice> or press <keycap>F5</keycap> . The elements listed in the Navigator vary with the document loaded in <productname>Writer</productname> ."
